        srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=300&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=89d1413db3c68a674edea29994fd9350 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=600&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=80409651aaa39b323aeef0bce5d75468 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=900&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1122581c78116df4161f765aeb33a808 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=975&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=a832424dd32b5592211bdeb4ec741d81 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=1088&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=fd644e7030840cc080ce61b3ddc37ad3 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=1200&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=8c9108e981bb742de749cd2a95fc5f28 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20250406-Reyes-Hurricane-Helene-Recovery-45_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.4842&amp;fp-y=0.371&amp;h=1500&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=9a4cd0c28f98e26c2287134250b5e678 2000w"
        style="object-position: 48.42% 37.1%;"        fetchpriority="high"    />


            
            
<figcaption class="attribution">
        <span class="attribution__caption">Susie and Brian Hill and their dog near their former home, destroyed by flooding from Hurricane Helene</span>
    
        <span class="attribution__credit">
        <span class="a11y">Credit: </span>
        Juan Diego Reyes for ProPublica
    </span>
    
    
    </figcaption>

        </figure>
            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper">

                    <span class="opener__topics">
            <a class="opener__topics-link" href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/environment">Environment</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1
        class="opener__hed "
        
    >        Arduous and Unequal: The Fight to Get FEMA Housing Assistance After Helene
    </h1>

    <h2
        class="opener__dek"
        style="display: none"        >
            An analysis by ProPublica and The Assembly of the more rural counties in North Carolina hardest hit by Helene shows that the households that got the most aid tended to have the highest incomes.
    </h2>
    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left     " data-pp-location="article meta">

    <span class="article-meta-1__byline" data-pp-location="article byine">
        by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a>, ProPublica, and <span class="name">Ren Larson</span>, <a href="https://www.theassemblync.com/">The Assembly</a>    </span>
    <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
        <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-09-27EDT05:10">Sept. 27, 2025, 5:10 a.m. EDT</time>
    </time>

    <div class="article-meta-1__section-actions
            " data-pp-location="article story-tools">
        
