                <div class="article-body__note article-body__note--correction">
            <span class="article-body__correction-label | wrap left size02 out02">Correction</span>
            <p><strong>Sept. 27, 2025:</strong> A video with this story originally misidentified the subject Brian Hill teaches. Hill teaches high school math, not history.</p>

