                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20221129-Teen-Motherhood-and-Teen-Abortion_02.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5849&amp;fp-y=0.3052&amp;h=267&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=3e98c6b5d2ac8a367f8d25ac215de9bb 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20221129-Teen-Motherhood-and-Teen-Abortion_02.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5849&amp;fp-y=0.3052&amp;h=533&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=5d666dbb6cab9115a97b73ac613fdae7 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20221129-Teen-Motherhood-and-Teen-Abortion_02.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5849&amp;fp-y=0.3052&amp;h=800&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=7dac6baa9a59347fb3f1a739dcd18a42 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20221129-Teen-Motherhood-and-Teen-Abortion_02.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5849&amp;fp-y=0.3052&amp;h=1067&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=5e57533ac558e8a1a8dfcfb7fed0aae9 1600w"
                    width="400"
                    height="267"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/post-roe-america">Post-Roe America</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/how-states-limit-teen-access-to-abortion">
                                    She Wanted an Abortion. A Judge Said She Wasn’t Mature Enough to Decide.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            As abortion access dwindles, America’s “parental-involvement” laws place further restrictions on teenagers — who may need to ask judges for permission to end their pregnancies.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lizzie-presser">Lizzie Presser</a>, photography by <span class="name">Parker Hill</span> and <span class="name">Isabel Bethencourt</span> for <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/">The New York Times</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2022-11-29EST05:00">Nov. 29, 2022, 5 a.m. EST</time>
            </span>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
            </div>
            </ol> <!-- end .most-read-group -->

</div> <!-- end .most-read -->

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

    
